cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.GR

This paper discusses the use of computer science technologies to create immersive digital worlds and process brain activity to infer inner states. This suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) as well as natural language processing (cs.CL) and cybernetics (cs.CY). Additionally, the use of digital worlds and storytelling may also fall under computer graphics (cs.GR).
